  "title": "Retail Associate (Core Duty Free)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet and assist customers, understand their needs and preferences</li>\n  <li>Provide product information and make recommendations</li>\n  <li>Promote and sell a wide range of duty-free products, such as liquor, tobacco, cosmetics, confectionery, and more</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the team to achieve sales targets and store objectives</li>\n  <li>Maintain organized and attractive product displays, restock shelves as needed, and keep the store tidy</li>\n  <li>Process transactions and manage payments</li>\n  <li>Assist with inventory management and support in stock taking activities</li>\n  <li>Adhere to store policies, procedures, and safety standard</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Previous experience in retail or customer service role is a plus</li>\n  <li>Excellent interpersonal and customer service skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under pressure and remain efficient during busy periods</li>\n  <li>Flexible to work various shifts, including weekends and public holidays</li>\n  <li>Ability to stand for extended periods of time</li>\n</ul>",
